-- India’s CBI Conducts Search of Former Minister Raja’s Homes
-- B y   S u b r a m a n i a m   S h a r m a
-- 2010-12-08T03:24:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/indian-investigators-search-former-telecom-minister-delhi-chennai-homes.html
India’s federal investigators
searched homes of former telecommunications minister Andimuthu
Raja in New Delhi and Chennai, R.K. Gaur, press information
officer of the Central Bureau of Investigation, said in a
telephone interview from New Delhi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
